---
layout: blog
---
%h1 Compass Blog Archive

- for post in blog_posts_in_order.reverse
  .post-snippet
    %h2
      - time = blog_date(post)
      %span.timestamp= time.strftime("%Y/%m/%d")
      %a{:href => post.rep_named(:default).path}= post[:title]
    %p= post[:intro] || post[:description]
  
    
